    "text": "Volunteer Driver Tax Appreciation Act of 2021\n\nThis bill increases the standard mileage rate for the tax deduction for the charitable use of a passenger automobile. The bill increases the rate from the standard charitable rate of 14 cents per mile to the standard business mileage rate (56 cents per mile in 2021)."
